        <footnote id="F5">The Incentive Units were awarded to the reporting person by CVR Energy, Inc., an affiliate of CVR Refining, LP, as compensation for services as an officer on December 18, 2015.  These Incentive Units vest ratably in three annual installments beginning in December of each year following the grant date, subject to the terms of the award agreement.</footnote>
